# data source: thoth_governance_cost_report

```terraform
data "thoth_governance_cost_report" "cost" {
  days = 30
  rate = 0.003
}
```

`response_json` includes the full payload, while typed fields expose pricing provenance:

- `pricing_source`, `pricing_version`, `pricing_sha256`, `pricing_updated_at`
- `priced_with_catalog_count`, `event_estimated_fallbacks`, `flat_rate_fallbacks`
- `unresolved_models`
